#what is splunk
splunk is a software platform widely used for searching,monitoring,analyzing and visualizing the mahine-generated data

splunk produces the graphs,alerts,dashboards and visualizations....

#why need to splunk
machine data is
      1)complex to understand
      2)unstructured format
      3)no suitable for analyzing and visualization
      4)It reduces the troubleshooting and resolving time by offering instant results
      5)Helps monitor to business metrics
#splunk products
    1)splunk enterprise
    2)splunk cloud
    3)splunk light
